name: Live Looping - Reel to Reel DIY Tape Loops & Effect Pedals
description: From found sounds recorded to DIY tape loops, play on tapedeck, process to effect pedals (looper, eq, delay, reverb). Create experimental music, build sounds of reel-to-reel tape loops, looping layer by layers, like architecture. [Don't forget to turn the sound on or unmute]. Created by @FahmiMursyid (Twitter). More info and updates : ideologikal.bandcamp.com
